    So show rule can accept _selectors_.
    
    There are lots of different selector types,
    for example
    
    - element functions
    - strings
    - regular expressions
    - field filters
    
    Let's see example of the latter:
    
    #show heading.where(level: 1): set align(center)
    
    = Title
    == Small title
    
