=  Location and sizes

We talked already about display and inline math. They differ not only by
aligning and spacing, but also by size and style:

    
    
    Inline: $a/(b + 1/c), sum_(n=0)^3 x_n$
    
    $
    a/(b + 1/c), sum_(n=0)^3 x_n
    $

