It is currently one of the _the darkest magics currently existing in Typst_ .
It gives you great powers, but with great power comes great responsibility.

==  Time travel

    
    
    #let s = state("x", 0)
    #let compute(expr) = [
      #s.update(x =>
        eval(expr.replace("x", str(x)))
