It is currently one of the _the darkest magics currently existing in Typst_ .
It gives you great powers, but with great power comes great responsibility.

==  Time travel

    
    
    #let s = state("x", 0)
    #let compute(expr) = [
      #s.update(x =>
        eval(expr.replace("x", str(x)))
      )
      New value is #s.display().
    ]
    
    Value at `<here>` is
    #context s.at(
      query(<here>)
        .first()
        .location()
    )
    
    #compute("10") \
    #compute("x + 3") \
    *Here.* <here> \
    #compute("x * 2") \
    #compute("x - 5")

