==  Semicolon syntax

When you use semicolons, the arguments _between the semicolons_ are merged
into arrays. See yourself:

    
    
    #let fun(..args) = {
        args.pos()
    }
    
    $
    fun(1, 2;3, 4; 6, ; 8)
    $

