img/7a3c90212650f7f7df0cb42177753236eddae675ac3220fbabd0f40e4af8b842-1.svg)

For example, this will not work:

    
    
    $
    //         ‚Üì there is no `;`, so it tries to add (gap:) to array
    mat(1, 2; 4, gap: #3em)
    $



