=  Fractional length

> Link to [ reference ](https://typst.app/docs/reference/layout/fraction/)

Single fraction length just takes _maximum size possible_ to fill the parent:

    
    
    Left #h(1fr) Right
    
    #rect(height: 1em)[
      #h(1fr)
    ]

